snippet.title: LEGO Brawls Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wise words of wisdom: When playing LEGO Brawls don't forget to block. 🧱️ 

LEGO Brawls launches September 2nd! 

Pre-order your copy now on Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Xbox Series X, PlayStation 4, or PlayStation 5!

Pre-Order: 
https://www.bandainamcoent.com/games/lego-brawls

Follow on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/LEGOBrawlsGame
